sentences.english: Silvereyes are omnivorous but have a particular fondness for fruit.
sentences.chinese: 灰胸绣眼鸟是杂食性的但是尤其喜爱食用植物的果实。

sentences.english: But I don’t care if you’re an omnivore.
sentences.chinese: 但是我也不会介意你是否是杂食动物。

sentences.english: The Great Bustard is polyphagia bird, but it feeds mainly on plants.
sentences.chinese: 大鸨是杂食性鸟类，但以植物性食物为主。

sentences.english: Most piranha species are omnivores and scavengers.
sentences.chinese: 绝大多数食人鱼类是杂食和食腐动物。

sentences.english: Omnivorous nocturnal mammal native to north and central america.
sentences.chinese: 原产于北美和中美夜间活动的杂食性哺乳动物。

sentences.english: But the omnivorous beast is rampant still.
sentences.chinese: 但是这只杂食动物依然毫无节制。
我是一个失败的杂食者。

sentences.english: The spines of the omnivorous pencil-spined urchin extend outward from its body.
sentences.chinese: 这个铅笔状的杂食性海胆的刺从它们的身体里伸出来。

sentences.english: I wanted to be an omnivore. I really did.
sentences.chinese: 真的，我确实曾想作一个杂食者。

sentences.english: I knew then that my days as an omnivore were numbered.
sentences.chinese: 我当时就知道，我作为一个杂食者的日子不多了。

sentences.english: The omnivorous White-Headed Weng has already gradually invaded the territory of the Wu-T'ou Weng.
sentences.chinese: 杂食性的白头翁已逐渐入侵乌头翁的领域。
毕竟，金鱼是杂食类动物。

sentences.english: The omnivorous, immobile beast is almost entirely concealed beneath the desert sands.
sentences.chinese: 这只不动的杂食野兽几乎完全隐藏在沙漠下。

sentences.english: He’s an 18)omnivore, and what a trainer would call food-driven.
sentences.chinese: 他是杂食动物，驯兽师称之为“食物驱动型”。

sentences.english: Keen to look at things from an omnivore's perspective, for balance.
sentences.chinese: 热衷于从杂食动物的角度来看，平衡看待事物。
